    Lisa:    5 points

    Step 7: Consensus reached - Story estimated at 5 points

    If no consensus after 2-3 rounds:
    - Take average or higher estimate
    - Or identify what's unclear and defer estimation
    */

    return conductVote(story, team);
  }

